---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
---

<Layout title="Terms of Service - DigitalStoreTrujillo">
    <Header />
    <div class="min-h-screen bg-background-dark py-12 px-4 lg:px-40">
        <div class="max-w-[900px] mx-auto">
            <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-8">Terms of Service</h1>

            <div
                class="bg-surface-dark border border-border-dark rounded-lg p-8 space-y-6 text-text-muted"
            >
                <section>
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
                        1. Acceptance of Terms
                    </h2>
                    <p class="mb-4">
                        By accessing and using DigitalStoreTrujillo, you accept
                        and agree to be bound by the terms and provision of this
                        agreement. If you do not agree to these terms, please do
                        not use our services.
                    </p>
                </section>

                <section>
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
                        2. Digital Products
                    </h2>
                    <p class="mb-4">
                        All products sold on DigitalStoreTrujillo are digital
                        goods, including but not limited to software licenses,
                        game keys, and digital services. These products are
                        delivered electronically and are non-physical items.
                    </p>
                    <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 ml-4">
                        <li>
                            Products are delivered via email or account
                            dashboard after payment confirmation
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            Activation keys and licenses are for personal use
                            only unless otherwise specified
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            Reselling or redistributing purchased products is
                            strictly prohibited
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            We are not responsible for compatibility issues with
                            your system
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </section>

                <section>
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
                        3. Payment and Pricing
                    </h2>
                    <p class="mb-4">
                        All prices are listed in USD and may be subject to
                        change without notice. We accept various payment methods
                        including:
                    </p>
                    <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 ml-4">
                        <li>Cryptocurrency payments via Cryptomus</li>
                        <li>Local payment methods (Yape, Binance Pay)</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p class="mt-4">
                        Payment must be completed before product delivery. All
                        sales are final unless otherwise stated in our Refund
                        Policy.
                    </p>
                </section>

                <section>
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
                        4. User Accounts
                    </h2>
                    <p class="mb-4">
                        When you create an account with us, you must provide
                        accurate and complete information. You are responsible
                        for:
                    </p>
                    <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 ml-4">
                        <li>
                            Maintaining the security of your account and
                            password
                        </li>
                        <li>All activities that occur under your account</li>
                        <li>
                            Notifying us immediately of any unauthorized use
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </section>

                <section>
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
                        5. Intellectual Property
                    </h2>
                    <p class="mb-4">
                        All content on DigitalStoreTrujillo, including text,
                        graphics, logos, and software, is the property of
                        DigitalStoreTrujillo or its content suppliers and is
                        protected by international copyright laws.
                    </p>
                </section>

                <section>
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
                        6. Prohibited Activities
                    </h2>
                    <p class="mb-4">You agree not to:</p>
                    <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 ml-4">
                        <li>Use our services for any illegal purpose</li>
                        <li>
                            Attempt to gain unauthorized access to our systems
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            Share, resell, or redistribute purchased products
                        </li>
                        <li>Use automated systems to access our services</li>
                        <li>Engage in fraudulent activities or chargebacks</li>
                    </ul>
                </section>

                <section>
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
                        7. Limitation of Liability
                    </h2>
                    <p class="mb-4">
                        DigitalStoreTrujillo shall not be liable for any
                        indirect, incidental, special, consequential, or
                        punitive damages resulting from your use or inability to
                        use our services.
                    </p>
                </section>

                <section>
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
                        8. Changes to Terms
                    </h2>
                    <p class="mb-4">
                        We reserve the right to modify these terms at any time.
                        Changes will be effective immediately upon posting to
                        the website. Your continued use of our services
                        constitutes acceptance of the modified terms.
                    </p>
                </section>

                <section>
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
                        9. Contact Information
                    </h2>
                    <p class="mb-4">
                        If you have any questions about these Terms of Service,
                        please contact us through our
                        <a href="/contact" class="text-primary hover:underline"
                            >Contact page</a
                        >.
                    </p>
                </section>

                <div class="mt-8 pt-6 border-t border-border-dark">
                    <p class="text-sm text-text-muted">
                        Last Updated: January 6, 2026
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <Footer />
</Layout>
